<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.8.3">
<l>cempoṉi laṅkuva laṅkaivāḷi tiṇcilai taṇṭoṭu caṅkamoḷvāḷ</l>
<l>umpari rucuṭa rāḻiyōṭu kēṭaka moṇmalar paṟṟiyeṟṟē</l>
<l>vempuci ṉattaṭal vēḻamvīḻa veṇmarup poṉṟupa ṟittiruṇṭa</l>
<l>vamputam pōṉṟiva rārkkoleṉṉa vaṭṭapu yakarat tēṉeṉṟārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As to the arrow, bright as fine gold [in] his strong hands,</l>
<l rend="indent">the powerful bow, with the mace, the conch, a bright sword,</l>
<l>With a discus [like] the great sun above, a shield [and] a radiant blossom,</l>
<l rend="indent">what a wonder!</l>
<l>When I asked, “Who is this appearing [like] a dark rain cloud,</l>
<l rend="indent">having plucked one white tusk</l>
<l rend="indent">so that a furious, enraged, battle elephant fell?”</l>
<l>He answered, “I am he in the house of the eight-armed [lord].”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
